1019
01:10:16,456 --> 01:10:19,876
- Good luck with your lecture.
- Thank you.

1020
01:10:27,967 --> 01:10:31,121
I want you all to imagine
you're at Cambridge University.

1021
01:10:31,221 --> 01:10:33,556
The year is 1807.

1022
01:10:33,681 --> 01:10:35,917
You walk across the quad
of Trinity College.

1023
01:10:36,017 --> 01:10:40,380
Into the lecture hall, you find
your fellow classmate, Lord Byron,

1024
01:10:40,480 --> 01:10:45,193
who, in defiance
of college rules about dogs,

1025
01:10:45,318 --> 01:10:48,446
has brought a bear to class instead.

1026
01:11:03,086 --> 01:11:05,296
You know what?

1027
01:11:05,880 --> 01:11:07,757
Forget about that.

1028
01:11:07,882 --> 01:11:11,636
Why are the Romantics relevant today?

1029
01:11:14,973 --> 01:11:16,724
Honestly...

1030
01:11:16,849 --> 01:11:18,518
they're not.

1031
01:11:19,978 --> 01:11:21,880
