1032
01:11:21,980 --> 01:11:26,134
And Dwight, he can't stop thinking
about home runs and fastballs

1033
01:11:26,234 --> 01:11:28,945
when he reads Byron and Coleridge.

1034
01:11:32,824 --> 01:11:34,492
Because...

1035
01:11:35,284 --> 01:11:37,370
we're teaching words.

1036
01:11:38,496 --> 01:11:40,123
Words.

1037
01:11:40,915 --> 01:11:43,459
