1038
01:11:45,044 --> 01:11:47,130
I got it all wrong.

1039
01:11:47,547 --> 01:11:52,009
I can tell you about Byron and his bear,
Wordsworth falling in love with his cousin,

1040
01:11:52,135 --> 01:11:55,455
