the words from them,

1042
01:11:59,058 --> 01:12:02,478
but I can't tell you what's behind
those words for you.

1043
01:12:03,354 --> 01:12:06,899
Because this class is about you

1044
01:12:07,024 --> 01:12:09,610
learning to find your own meaning.

1045
01:12:10,945 --> 01:12:13,030
