I would prefer cash.

1066
01:13:44,622 --> 01:13:47,358
Wanted to be the first
to congratulate you.

1067
01:13:47,458 --> 01:13:50,570
Welcome to the English department,
University of Los Angeles.

1068
01:13:50,670 --> 01:13:52,697
Yes!

1069
01:13:52,797 --> 01:13:55,658
Oh, good. Oh, thank you, boss.

1070
01:13:55,758 --> 01:13:57,927
I guess we'll do the other side as well.

1071
01:13:58,052 --> 01:14:00,454
- Let's go have a pint.
- A pint of what? Oil?

1072
01:14:00,554 --> 01:14:04,642
