1093
01:15:51,791 --> 01:15:55,361
Strike two, you failed
the recovery program.

1094
01:15:55,461 --> 01:15:58,030
We may be 0-2, but we're going
to swing for the fences

1095
01:15:58,130 --> 01:16:00,466
