You remember my epitaph.

1171
01:22:47,163 --> 01:22:49,124
Of course I do, Dad.

1172
01:22:50,500 --> 01:22:52,711
Of course I do.

1173
01:23:54,481 --> 01:23:57,942
Byzantium is the place he longs for.

1174
01:23:58,276 --> 01:24:00,595
