I love most in this world.

1254
01:32:09,516 --> 01:32:13,020
- Even you, Brian.
- You're the man, Richard.

1255
01:32:13,395 --> 01:32:17,341
There comes a time, and there's always
a time, and I guess this is the time.

1256
01:32:17,441 --> 01:32:21,487
So, Jakey, shall we set grandpa free?

1257
01:32:30,204 --> 01:32:32,247
Okay, Dad.

1258
01:32:32,873 --> 01:32:35,167
Enjoy paradise.

1259
